Description
	This is a simple server-client program using UDP sockets for the transmission. Basically the client sends a message to the server, the server converts the message to uppercase and returns it to the client.

Note: Please run Server first in one terminal and client in another terminal

Steps to compile
[1] make
	complites both server.c and client.c
[2] make clean
	clean up

Output ./client 
Type a sentence to send to server:
hello
You typed: hello
Received from server: HELLO

